snippet.title: ＢＳスーパーマリオコレクション 第３週 | BS Super Mario Collection 3
snippet.description:
Took a small break from Excitebike-ness.

I'm really normally better at SMB games than this, but recording/input lag and keyboard controls are fairly off-putting for me.

Yes, my head nearly popped when my time ran out -right on Bowser-.

As with the Excitebike games, BS Super Mario Collection Dai-3-shuu has no BGM.
